### Environment Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
@userToken = YOUR_USER_OR_ORGANIZER_JWT_TOKEN

@ticketId = TKT-XXXXXX-XXX


### =========================================================================
### 1. USER & ORGANIZER ACTIONS
### =========================================================================

### Create Support Ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/support/create
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Billing",
  "subject": "Double charged for Event Booking",
  "description": "I checked my bank statement and noticed that my account was debited twice for the last booking.",
  "images": [""]
}

### Get My Tickets (with optional pagination & filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/support/my-tickets?page=1&limit=10&status=Pending
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Support Ticket Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/support/{{ticketId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Reopen Support Ticket (User Side)
POST {{baseUrl}}/support/update/{{ticketId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Reopen"
}

### Close Support Ticket (User Side)
POST {{baseUrl}}/support/update/{{ticketId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "closed"
}


### =========================================================================
### 2. ADMIN ACTIONS
### =========================================================================

### Admin: Get All Tickets (with filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/support/admin/list?page=1&limit=10&status=Pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Admin: Update Ticket Status & Add Comment
POST {{baseUrl}}/support/admin/update/{{ticketId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Resolved",
  "adminComment": "We have processed the refund. Please allow 3-5 business days for it to reflect."
}

